OL,3,CCounty Durham boxing club nominated
OL,4,Cfor national community impact award
OL,6,FA Ferryhill boxing club has been
OL,7,Fpraised for changing young lives, Kris
OL,8,FJepson reports
OL,10,FA County Durham boxing club is in the
OL,11,Frunning for a prestigious boxing award
OL,12,Fafter being shortlisted from more than
OL,13,Fone thousand clubs across the country.
OL,15,FMainsforth Amateur Boxing and Fitness
OL,16,FClub was set up in Ferryhill in County
OL,17,FDurham by Richard O'Neill, aimed at
OL,18,Fsupporting his autistic daughter.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
