OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784535494
OL,3,CCounty Durham boxing club nominated
OL,4,Cfor national community impact award
OL,6,FIt has now been shortlisted as one of
OL,7,Fthe top three clubs for community
OL,8,Fimpact at the England Boxing Annual
OL,9,FAwards.
OL,11,FIn just four years, the club has also
OL,12,Fhelped change the lives of many young
OL,13,Fpeople in the community.
OL,15,FMr O'Neill told ITV News Tyne Tees:
OL,16,F"Boxing changed my life. I know how
OL,17,Fmuch my little girl has grown in here
OL,18,Fas well, herself".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
