PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784535494
OL,3,CCounty Durham boxing club nominated
OL,4,Cfor national community impact award
OL,6,FHe said that the award nomination was
OL,7,F"absolutely brilliant" and would make
OL,8,Fa real difference to the area.
OL,10,F"It is a deprived area," he said, "it
OL,11,Fis going to give Ferryhill what it
OL,12,Fneeds. It needs that boost and these
OL,13,Fchildren are looking up to us, as
OL,14,Fcoaches, and we are like role models
OL,15,Fto them."
OL,17,FThe club offers a community gym for
OL,18,Fpeople aged anywhere between six-years-
OL,19,Fold and 80.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
