PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784535494
OL,3,CCounty Durham boxing club nominated
OL,4,Cfor national community impact award
OL,6,FOne of the youth members told ITV Tyne
OL,7,FTees that the club has helped people
OL,8,Fgain "direction in life".
OL,10,FHe said: "People like within the
OL,11,Fcommunity who've had no direction in
OL,12,Flife, being given direction, being
OL,13,Fgiven a purpose and drive to work
OL,14,Ftowards being a better person."
OL,16,FAnother young boxer said: "It's made
OL,17,Fme the person I am today. It's given
OL,18,Fme confidence, discipline, but also,
OL,19,FI've made new friends, I've gained
OL,20,Ffitness, strength and confidence in
OL,21,Fmyself."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
