OL,3,CCounty Durham boxing club nominated
OL,4,Cfor national community impact award
OL,6,FThe club is also now providing
OL,7,Falternative education sessions for
OL,8,Fchildren who have been excluded from
OL,9,Fmainstream school.
OL,11,F"We're doing great things with them
OL,12,F(the children), Mr O'Neill said. "They
OL,13,Fjust need a bit of structure and
OL,14,Fpositive people around them to help
OL,15,Fthem. When we talk to them, we are
OL,16,Flike mentors with them and we're
OL,17,Fbuilding with them."
